{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a subscription page for Unchained Coffee that mirrors the structure and UX of the Onyx Coffee Lab subscription page, adapted to Unchained’s brand.
    
    Required structure:
    
    Subscription Level Selection
    
    Display three selectable subscription products:
    Starter, Shifter, Breaker
    
    Each level is a separate Shopify product.
    
    Quantity per Shipment
    
    Variant selector with: 250g and 1kg
    
    Subscription Type Toggle
    
    Option A: Subscribe by Frequency (weekly / bi-weekly / monthly)
    
    Option B: Subscribe by Usage (usage-based / smart reorder description)
    
    Gift Subscription Section
    
    “This is a gift” toggle
    
    Shipment count options: 3 / 6 / 12 shipments
    
    Primary CTA
    
    Main button: Add to Cart / Subscribe
    
    UX & Style:
    
    Clean, minimal, structured layout
    
    Step-by-step selection flow (level → quantity → type → gift → CTA)
    
    Clear headings and short microcopy
    
    Tone:
    
    Premium, direct, Unchained voice (bold, transparent, no fluff)
    
    Output:
    
    Generate publish-ready section titles, labels, and CTA text following this structure.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
